nodes.text: Rannos was a male Human agent of the Republic Strategic Information Service who held the position of Chief during the Galactic War. When the Tion Hegemony was overtaken by an outbreak of the rakghoul plague, Rannos grew concerned and dispatched his operative Whisper to recruit aid.
Chief Rannos introduces Republic players to the Kaon Under Siege Flashpoint, which was added to the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic in Game Update 1.1. He is voiced by Fred Tatasciore.
